U||   Letter, Dr. Seward to Hon. Arthur Holmwood.
U||   “6 September.
U||   “My dear Art,—
U||   “My news to-day is not so good. Lucy this morning had gone back a bit.
U||   There is, however, one good thing which has arisen from it; Mrs.
