U||   you trust, and trust cannot be where there is mean nature. And your
U||   husband—tell me of him. Is he quite well? Is all that fever gone, and
U||   is he strong and hearty?” I saw here an opening to ask him about
U||   Jonathan, so I said:—
U||   “He was almost recovered, but he has been greatly upset by Mr.
U||   Hawkins’s death.” He interrupted:—
