U||   relief when we saw the Professor calmly restoring the strings of putty
U||   to the edges of the door.
U||   When this was done, he lifted the child and said:
U||   “Come now, my friends; we can do no more till to-morrow. There is a
U||   funeral at noon, so here we shall all come before long after that. The
U||   friends of the dead will all be gone by two, and when the sexton lock
U||   the gate we shall remain. Then there is more to do; but not like this
