U||   who has a better right? Will it be no joy to think of hereafter in the
U||   silence of the night when sleep is not: ‘It was my hand that sent her
U||   to the stars; it was the hand of him that loved her best; the hand that
U||   of all she would herself have chosen, had it been to her to choose?’
