U||   We all looked at Arthur. He saw, too, what we all did, the infinite
U||   kindness which suggested that his should be the hand which would
U||   restore Lucy to us as a holy, and not an unholy, memory; he stepped
U||   forward and said bravely, though his hand trembled, and his face was as
