U||   “My true friend, from the bottom of my broken heart I thank you. Tell
U||   me what I am to do, and I shall not falter!” Van Helsing laid a hand on
U||   his shoulder, and said:—
U||   “Brave lad! A moment’s courage, and it is done. This stake must be
U||   driven through her. It will be a fearful ordeal—be not deceived in
U||   that—but it will be only a short time, and you will then rejoice more
