U||   rest. We have seen it with our eyes.
U||   “Thus when we find the habitation of this man-that-was, we can confine
U||   him to his coffin and destroy him, if we obey what we know. But he is
U||   clever. I have asked my friend Arminius, of Buda-Pesth University, to
U||   make his record; and, from all the means that are, he tell me of what
U||   he has been. He must, indeed, have been that Voivode Dracula who won
U||   his name against the Turk, over the great river on the very frontier of
