U||   “No, sir. But ye needn’t have no difficulty about that. It’s a ’igh ’un
U||   with a stone front with a bow on it, an’ ’igh steps up to the door. I
U||   know them steps, ’avin’ ’ad to carry the boxes up with three loafers
