U||   means discovered of gaining access to the house.
U||   There was at present nothing to be learned from the Piccadilly side,
U||   and nothing could be done; so I went round to the back to see if
U||   anything could be gathered from this quarter. The mews were active, the
U||   Piccadilly houses being mostly in occupation. I asked one or two of the
U||   grooms and helpers whom I saw around if they could tell me anything
U||   about the empty house. One of them said that he heard it had lately
U||   been taken, but he couldn’t say from whom. He told me, however, that up
